Description: Kong cortical parcellation atlases for the 'ggsegverse'
    ecosystem. Includes the Kong 2019 MS-HBM 17-network atlas and
    the Kong 2022 Areal MS-HBM 17-network parcellations at resolutions
    from 100 to 1000 parcels. Provides 'ggseg_atlas' objects with 2D
    polygon geometry and 3D vertex indices.
